Job Description:
This is a part-time and remote job for Research Scientist in Machine Learning ( or Artificial Intelligence ). A Ph.D. degree is required.
AAFIE Artificial Intelligence Labs at AAFIE focuses on the research and development of digital transformation solutions for manufacturing and healthcare industries. Our founding members include AI professors from UC Berkeley & Purdue as well as senior engineers from Silicon Valley. Accomplishing our mission requires doing really big things for customers. We are currently looking for innovative, collaborative and curious people who love to solve real-world challenging problems in various industries using machine learning and AI.
Primary Responsibilities:
Conduct research and development projects in machine learning and artificial intelligence;
Collaborate with domain experts in industry to identify critical challenges and opportunities for AI-driven improvements, and prioritize projects accordingly;

